		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You have gained substantial knowledge about the connections between the elements and the divine. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain proficiency with the Arcana skill or an expertise die if you are already proficient. You also gain the Elementals skill specialty for Arcana, or another of your choice if you already have it. It does not count against your skill specialties known.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain proficiency with the Primordial and Celestial languages. If you are already proficient with one of the languages, you can choose another from the following list instead: Aquan, Auran, Draconic, Ignan, Infernal, or Terran.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Half your cleric levels count as elementalist levels for the purpose of determining the damage done by your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.uit7l3mc64l5h8h1]{Elemental Blast}.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Half your cleric levels count as elementalist levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.z2q6kb24eks8nfy5]{Expand Element} feature.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
